GCF columnar format (internal/gcf):
The GCF "generic profile" text format implemented in internal/gcf originates
from gcf-typescript, Copyright (c) Blackwell Systems
(https://github.com/blackwell-systems/gcf-typescript), licensed under the MIT
License, as vendored into OmniRoute
(https://github.com/diegosouzapw/OmniRoute), also MIT-licensed. internal/gcf
is an independent Go reimplementation of the format (scalars-only subset);
no upstream source code was copied.
